translation[8]{c,v,t}:
  8,9,"(Nikhumbule) okokuba nina nacela uncedo eNkosini yenu Yaza Yaniphendula (Isithi): “Ndiya kunincedisa ngewaka leengelosi, enye emva kwenye zilandelelana"
  8,10,"UAllâh Wakwenza oko ukuba kube ziindaba ezivuyisayo, kwanokuba iintliziyo zenu zibe sekuphumleni ngako oko. Kananjalo alukho uloyiso ngaphandle koluvela kuAllâh. Inene uAllâh nguSomandla, uSobulumko"
  8,11,"Nikhumbule kananjalo okokuba Yena Wanigquma ngobuthongo ukuba bube lukhuseleko lwenu, Wenza namanzi (emvula) ukuba ehle phezu kwenu esuka esibhakabhakeni, ukunihlambulula ngawo, Asuse iingcinga zokungcola zikaShaytân kuni, nokunomeleza iintliziyo zenu, Wanomeleza neenyawo zenu"
  8,12,"Khumbulani kananjalo okokuba iNkosi yenu Yatyhila kwiingelosi (Yathi): “Mna Ndikunye nani, ke yomelezani abo bakholwayo. Ndiya kufaka ixhala ezintliziyweni zabo bangakholwayo, bageceni ke ezintanyeni, nibaxabele iminwe yabo yonke neenzwane (zabo).”"
  8,13,"Oku kungenxa yokuba baye badelela abaMthobela uAllâh noMthunywa waKhe. Nabani na ke lowo udelela, angaMthobeli uAllâh noMthunywa waKhe, kulowo Wohlwaya kabuhlungu uAllâh"
  8,14,"Esi sisohlwayo senu, singcamleni ke; kananjalo inene kwabo bangakholwayo iya kuba sisohlwayo soMlilo"
  8,15,"Hininaninabakholwayo! Xanihlangenenabobangakholwayo edabini, ningaze nijike nize ngomva kubo"
  8,16,"Ke lowo uthe wabazela ngomva ngemini enjengaleyo ngaphandle kokuba uya kuba ehlenga-hlengisa ngendlela yemfazwe, okanye ehlehla umva esiya kumabutho (ecala lakhe), uya kuba uzitsalela ingqumbo ka-Allâh. Kanti nekhaya lakhe liya kuba sisiHogo, hayi ububi besiphelo solo hambo"